---

<Base>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-blue-100 py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
              Tired of productivity systems that don't fit? It's time you built your own.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto opacity-90 animate-fade-in">
              Discover how to experiment, shape, and craft a personalized system that empowers the life you truly want to live.
          </p>
          <div class="text-center"> <!-- Centering the single button -->
              <a href="#" class="bg-orange-300 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-orange-400 transition duration-300 ease-in-out text-lg font-bold">
                  Download Starter Guide
              </a>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

    <!-- Problem Statement Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
                You've invested time and effort into every popular task manager and expert's framework, only to find them rigid, incomplete, or simply not aligned with how <em class="font-semibold">you</em> work.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                That nagging feeling persists:
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                Why does everyone else's system seem to work, but yours falls short?
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Your Unique Path to Productivity Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">Your Unique Path to Productivity</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
                The reason those "perfect" systems never quite work for you is simple: <strong class="font-semibold">productivity is deeply personal.</strong> You'll never achieve your full potential by adopting someone else's personalized framework. They built it for them, not you.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                My approach isn't about teaching you <em class="font-semibold">my</em> specific system; it's about guiding you through a simple process to <strong class="font-semibold">craft a perfectly tailored productivity system to meet your needs.</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How I Help You Build Your System Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">How I Help You Build <em class="italic">Your</em> System</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            <!-- Service 1: Productivity Pals -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-blue-600 mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h2a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4 0V4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v2M4 9v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2zm6-6h.01"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-center mb-4 text-gray-900">Productivity Pals</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
                    You don't have to journey towards perfect productivity alone! Join Productivity Pals, a small, yet growing community dedicated to building and perfecting personalized productivity systems. Connect with like-minded individuals, share real-world insights, and actively hone your personalized productivity system alongside supportive peers.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <a href="https://productivitypals.creadevlabs.com" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-green-400 text-green-900 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-green-500 transition duration-300">Join Today!</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 2: Sunstone Academy -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-blue-600 mb-4">
                    <!-- Placeholder icon for Sunstone Academy -->
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-center mb-4 text-gray-900">Sunstone Academy</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
                    Transform your daily tasks into an engaging adventure! Sunstone Academy is a gamified task manager app set in a magical school, designed to make productivity fun and rewarding. It's also a highly flexible task manager, allowing you to adapt it to your unique workflow. Gather resources, unlock achievements, and level up your life as you complete your to-do list.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsntwn2ixQrM6njdiIoIgbA8HgqJqtE0N&si=Z1wC2oPdu8-MN31l" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-yellow-900 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-500 transition duration-300">See Development Progress</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 3: The Obsidian Productivity Masterclass: Craft Your Own Perfect System -->
            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-blue-600 mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-center mb-4 text-gray-900">The Obsidian Productivity Masterclass: Craft Your Own Perfect System</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
                    Tired of systems that don't stick? This course combines <strong class="font-semibold">Obsidian's powerful, flexible features</strong> with my <strong class="font-semibold">step-by-step framework</strong> to help you craft one that does. Learn the basics of Obsidian and then apply a proven process to design, implement, and optimize a productivity system uniquely tailored to your needs, so you can finally get things done, your way.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-yellow-900 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-500 transition duration-300">Join the Waitlist</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center bg-white p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The time to build your perfect productivity system is now</h2>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Join me and a growing community of individuals using my simple framework to design a system that truly works for them.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="bg-orange-300 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-orange-400 transition duration-300 ease-in-out text-xl font-bold inline-flex items-center group">
              Download my free starter guide today
              <svg class="ml-3 w-6 h-6 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
          </a>
      </div>
    </section>

